<section class="warehouse-network" aria-label="东南亚仓储与发货规则可视化">
  <header class="network-header">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">WAREHOUSE ROUTING</span>
      <h2>4 个仓库，形成一套“本地优先、跨境兜底”的履约网络</h2>
      <p>三个国家各有独立雅仓；深圳跨境仓由三国共用，但只在本国雅仓无可用库存时接手发货。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="network-metrics" aria-label="仓储网络概览">
      <span><b>3</b> 个国家</span>
      <span><b>3</b> 个雅仓</span>
      <span><b>2</b> 个平台</span>
      <span><b>1</b> 个跨境仓</span>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="country-grid">
    <article class="country-card country-th">
      <div class="country-heading">
        <span class="country-code">TH</span>
        <div>
          <strong>泰国雅仓</strong>
          <small>仅服务泰国站点</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stock-pool">
        <span class="pool-label">本国实物库存</span>
        <strong>同一份库存池</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="platform-row">
        <span class="platform-chip shopee">Shopee</span>
        <span class="share-mark">共享</span>
        <span class="platform-chip lazada">Lazada</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="country-card country-my">
      <div class="country-heading">
        <span class="country-code">MY</span>
        <div>
          <strong>马来西亚雅仓</strong>
          <small>仅服务马来西亚站点</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stock-pool">
        <span class="pool-label">本国实物库存</span>
        <strong>同一份库存池</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="platform-row">
        <span class="platform-chip shopee">Shopee</span>
        <span class="share-mark">共享</span>
        <span class="platform-chip lazada">Lazada</span>
      </div>
    </article>

    <article class="country-card country-ph">
      <div class="country-heading">
        <span class="country-code">PH</span>
        <div>
          <strong>菲律宾雅仓</strong>
          <small>仅服务菲律宾站点</small>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="stock-pool">
        <span class="pool-label">本国实物库存</span>
        <strong>同一份库存池</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="platform-row">
        <span class="platform-chip shopee">Shopee</span>
        <span class="share-mark">共享</span>
        <span class="platform-chip lazada">Lazada</span>
      </div>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="boundary-strip">
    <span class="boundary-icon" aria-hidden="true">×</span>
    <div>
      <strong>国家之间不共享库存</strong>
      <p>泰国、马来西亚、菲律宾三地雅仓是独立物理库房。一国有货，不代表另外两国可以调用。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="boundary-codes" aria-label="三国库存相互隔离">
      <span>TH</span><i></i><span>MY</span><i></i><span>PH</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="route-board">
    <div class="route-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">SHIPPING PRIORITY</span>
      <h3>发货只看一个优先级</h3>
      <p>先检查订单所在国家的本地雅仓；只有本地没有可用库存，才切换到深圳跨境仓。</p>
    </div>

    <div class="route-flow" aria-label="发货优先级流程">
      <div class="route-node primary">
        <span>优先</span>
        <strong>本国雅仓</strong>
        <small>有可用库存</small>
      </div>
      <span class="route-arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
      <div class="route-result success">
        <span>本地履约</span>
        <strong>直接发货</strong>
      </div>
      <span class="route-divider">无可用库存 ↓</span>
      <div class="route-node fallback">
        <span>兜底</span>
        <strong>深圳跨境仓</strong>
        <small>三国共用直发渠道</small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="platform-aliases">
    <div class="alias-intro">
      <span class="eyebrow">BACKEND NAMES</span>
      <strong>当前业务后台名称</strong>
      <small>这里记录的是当前操作口径，不代表所有平台、所有商家都只有这一种叫法。</small>
    </div>
    <div class="alias-card lazada-alias">
      <span>Lazada 后台</span>
      <strong>3PF</strong>
    </div>
    <div class="alias-card shopee-alias">
      <span>Shopee 后台</span>
      <strong>LFF</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

